ofxDmxUtils motion-Kinect Example
=====================================

this is a very simple example showing how to connect MS Kinect's hand tracking capabilities with Dmx using ofxDmxUtils::setRotation


Installation
------------
please add ofxDmxUtils, ofxDmx and ofxOpenNI (2.0) to the addons folder.
don't forget to include the openni lib and config folders in the bin/data/openni folder.

